{"tid":50800,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"北海道行程一問","createTime":"2016-12-22T17:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-14T08:07:11.000Z","uid":34299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7e3b1eaa8decb2e5036e25f1de65a434983fc12","tid":50800,"uid":34299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:11:03.000Z","msg":"我黎緊會同屋企人去北海道<br />\n我地大概嘅行程係頭兩晚登別<br />\n第三至五晚喺札幌過<br />\n<br />\n問想下如果我地去旭川動物園好唔好？<br />\n因為車飛都幾貴 同埋要搭好耐車去<br />\n<br />\n仲有 我地喺札幌個幾日會去埋小樽 <br />\n如果係咁嘅話買唔買個啲jr pass 好？"},{"pid":"045fd0ad1e744b43bdf4ecd0b6c1fda814eac47c","tid":50800,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:11:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52d3def5c9c205c50f1edeed0d519f464c3f7df1","tid":50800,"uid":34299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:17:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c10c4f6c7811986b372d8320f661f0e1d882c21","tid":50800,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:23:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我黎緊會同屋企人去北海道<br />\n我地大概嘅行程係頭兩晚登別<br />\n第三至五晚喺札幌過<br />\n<br />\n問想下如果我地去旭川動物園好唔好？<br />\n因為車飛都幾貴 同埋要搭好耐車去<br />\n<br />\n仲有 我地喺札幌個幾日會去埋小樽 <br />\n如果係咁嘅話買唔買個啲jr pass 好？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小樽有個乜鬼welcome pass...1700 yen 一個人<br />\n一日札幌 - 小樽 jr 同札幌市內地下鐵任搭"},{"pid":"ee6b06a69f738939dafda1eae2f9535a7115a5cb","tid":50800,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:33:33.000Z","msg":"如果你去埋函館可以jr pass 會抵d<br />\n<br />\n但兩日登別，三日札幌就唔太抵咁...<br />\n<br />\n反正你小樽同旭川都各用左一日...最後一日札幌你都唔會去得邊<br />\n<br />\n自己計下啦 3日JR pass 都要16500yen...有可能買pass 好d 啵<br />\n<br />\n旭川動物園都有個套票<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.jrhokkaido.co.jp/global/pdf/tw/asahiyama201611.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.jrhokkaido.co.jp%2Fglobal%2Fpdf%2Ftw%2Fasahiyama201611.pdf&d=puiSddp9Vo3i8vVDNE0kXUsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=f47c6fdf\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.jrhokkaido.co.jp/global/pdf/tw/asahiyama201611.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n小樽pass<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.jrhokkaido.co.jp/global/chinese/railpass/welcome.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.jrhokkaido.co.jp%2Fglobal%2Fchinese%2Frailpass%2Fwelcome.pdf&d=puiSddp9Vo3i8vVDNE0kXUsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=44dc2a0d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.jrhokkaido.co.jp/global/chinese/railpass/welcome.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"2f3435934898a4c875d317435d0e7ad6f6a6eee7","tid":50800,"uid":34299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:33:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我黎緊會同屋企人去北海道<br />\n我地大概嘅行程係頭兩晚登別<br />\n第三至五晚喺札幌過<br />\n<br />\n問想下如果我地去旭川動物園好唔好？<br />\n因為車飛都幾貴 同埋要搭好耐車去<br />\n<br />\n仲有 我地喺札幌個幾日會去埋小樽 <br />\n如果係咁嘅話買唔買個啲jr pass 好？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小樽有個乜鬼welcome pass...1700 yen 一個人<br />\n一日札幌 - 小樽 jr 同札幌市內地下鐵任搭</blockquote><br />\n即係一日內札幌同小樽所以jr任搭？<br />\n係咪要去到先買 <br />\nthx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e9d84610252381c34f2ea213c46bb4981e92138","tid":50800,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:43:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我黎緊會同屋企人去北海道<br />\n我地大概嘅行程係頭兩晚登別<br />\n第三至五晚喺札幌過<br />\n<br />\n問想下如果我地去旭川動物園好唔好？<br />\n因為車飛都幾貴 同埋要搭好耐車去<br />\n<br />\n仲有 我地喺札幌個幾日會去埋小樽 <br />\n如果係咁嘅話買唔買個啲jr pass 好？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小樽有個乜鬼welcome pass...1700 yen 一個人<br />\n一日札幌 - 小樽 jr 同札幌市內地下鐵任搭</blockquote><br />\n即係一日內札幌同小樽所以jr任搭？<br />\n係咪要去到先買 <br />\nthx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新千歲機場有jr counter...個到有得買<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 我無去過登別 唔知點搭車...你最好自己計下點買先抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b203824cd078fadc6634a62ce136e6ec44bc900","tid":50800,"uid":64514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T19:09:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我黎緊會同屋企人去北海道<br />\n我地大概嘅行程係頭兩晚登別<br />\n第三至五晚喺札幌過<br />\n<br />\n問想下如果我地去旭川動物園好唔好？<br />\n因為車飛都幾貴 同埋要搭好耐車去<br />\n<br />\n仲有 我地喺札幌個幾日會去埋小樽 <br />\n如果係咁嘅話買唔買個啲jr pass 好？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n登別一日夠 <br />\n如果你只去南邊其實唔洗買pass  圍返其實唔貴<br />\n動物園無去 去左個大雪山 好靚"},{"pid":"b47e0761dd5be67dd507a87972aa2c4646657a87","tid":50800,"uid":34299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T19:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我黎緊會同屋企人去北海道<br />\n我地大概嘅行程係頭兩晚登別<br />\n第三至五晚喺札幌過<br />\n<br />\n問想下如果我地去旭川動物園好唔好？<br />\n因為車飛都幾貴 同埋要搭好耐車去<br />\n<br />\n仲有 我地喺札幌個幾日會去埋小樽 <br />\n如果係咁嘅話買唔買個啲jr pass 好？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小樽有個乜鬼welcome pass...1700 yen 一個人<br />\n一日札幌 - 小樽 jr 同札幌市內地下鐵任搭</blockquote><br />\n即係一日內札幌同小樽所以jr任搭？<br />\n係咪要去到先買 <br />\nthx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新千歲機場有jr counter...個到有得買<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 我無去過登別 唔知點搭車...你最好自己計下點買先抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n登別個到有巴士直到札幌 所以呢個唔洗諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打你上面旭川套票話咩四日有效 係咪指唔包門票個個？"},{"pid":"47147de02c961155c60e39d5ea513f5f032484b6","tid":50800,"uid":34299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T19:50:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我黎緊會同屋企人去北海道<br />\n我地大概嘅行程係頭兩晚登別<br />\n第三至五晚喺札幌過<br />\n<br />\n問想下如果我地去旭川動物園好唔好？<br />\n因為車飛都幾貴 同埋要搭好耐車去<br />\n<br />\n仲有 我地喺札幌個幾日會去埋小樽 <br />\n如果係咁嘅話買唔買個啲jr pass 好？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n登別一日夠 <br />\n如果你只去南邊其實唔洗買pass  圍返其實唔貴<br />\n動物園無去 去左個大雪山 好靚</blockquote><br />\n大雪山即係大雪山國立公園 定係咩旭岳纜車<br />\n定其實佢地係同一樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"420ae843bcd76508ee13578e0fea897ea46ef9a7","tid":50800,"uid":64514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T19:57:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我黎緊會同屋企人去北海道<br />\n我地大概嘅行程係頭兩晚登別<br />\n第三至五晚喺札幌過<br />\n<br />\n問想下如果我地去旭川動物園好唔好？<br />\n因為車飛都幾貴 同埋要搭好耐車去<br />\n<br />\n仲有 我地喺札幌個幾日會去埋小樽 <br />\n如果係咁嘅話買唔買個啲jr pass 好？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n登別一日夠 <br />\n如果你只去南邊其實唔洗買pass  圍返其實唔貴<br />\n動物園無去 去左個大雪山 好靚</blockquote><br />\n大雪山即係大雪山國立公園 定係咩旭岳纜車<br />\n定其實佢地係同一樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大雪山其實好大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  旭岳纜車只係帶到你去山腰個啲， 好多人會喺個到開始行上去 當然行上山頂無可能 除非專業行山 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係係好靚  有好多湖結冰 同埋望返上山頂好靚 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Agz1X27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAgz1X27.jpg&h=f81df79c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/035651_2fd57aa2529942773833b1d3c06eeb42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F035651_2fd57aa2529942773833b1d3c06eeb42.jpg&h=f7412550&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQ38h6Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQ38h6Y.jpg&h=1fca2b5b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6iP7Jcf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6iP7Jcf.jpg&h=4814eccb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ca65bef9d304aa57838f6bcf2399448bbf03335","tid":50800,"uid":64514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T20:00:02.000Z","msg":"去唔去埋美瑛個邊？ 好撚靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/035842_b184fecff8f78c0888155842a35b68ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F035842_b184fecff8f78c0888155842a35b68ec.jpg&h=7996609b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/035843_b184fecff8f78c0888155842a35b68ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F035843_b184fecff8f78c0888155842a35b68ec.jpg&h=9181f03a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/035843_f821523dc51623e8ccfc9bfa857eec98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F035843_f821523dc51623e8ccfc9bfa857eec98.jpg&h=95cd6625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冬天仲靚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 旭岳好多拉麵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個到係拉麵集中地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35bd39b5e72b42e6d47f35d844faa970ee1b3c72","tid":50800,"uid":64514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T20:07:30.000Z","msg":"其實搭去旭岳都唔係好耐 好快過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n睇巴打你同屋企人想睇咩啦 <br />\n自然景 登別有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  向北 旭川 美瑛 好正 <br />\n札榥多野買 狸小路有間居酒屋好撚好食 平靚正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但景點黎講我自己覺得唔特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae8501a7e7afc3932e4c3da1645792bf08505ae","tid":50800,"uid":34299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T02:55:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我黎緊會同屋企人去北海道<br />\n我地大概嘅行程係頭兩晚登別<br />\n第三至五晚喺札幌過<br />\n<br />\n問想下如果我地去旭川動物園好唔好？<br />\n因為車飛都幾貴 同埋要搭好耐車去<br />\n<br />\n仲有 我地喺札幌個幾日會去埋小樽 <br />\n如果係咁嘅話買唔買個啲jr pass 好？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n登別一日夠 <br />\n如果你只去南邊其實唔洗買pass  圍返其實唔貴<br />\n動物園無去 去左個大雪山 好靚</blockquote><br />\n大雪山即係大雪山國立公園 定係咩旭岳纜車<br />\n定其實佢地係同一樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大雪山其實好大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  旭岳纜車只係帶到你去山腰個啲， 好多人會喺個到開始行上去 當然行上山頂無可能 除非專業行山 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係係好靚  有好多湖結冰 同埋望返上山頂好靚 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Agz1X27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAgz1X27.jpg&h=f81df79c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/035651_2fd57aa2529942773833b1d3c06eeb42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F035651_2fd57aa2529942773833b1d3c06eeb42.jpg&h=f7412550&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQ38h6Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQ38h6Y.jpg&h=1fca2b5b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6iP7Jcf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6iP7Jcf.jpg&h=4814eccb&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我老豆屌鳩我話搭車去到老練咁遠淨係睇雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae8c430c0be251f2e68cdb49b8feb8f7159032e","tid":50800,"uid":34299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T02:59:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實搭去旭岳都唔係好耐 好快過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n睇巴打你同屋企人想睇咩啦 <br />\n自然景 登別有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  向北 旭川 美瑛 好正 <br />\n札榥多野買 狸小路有間居酒屋好撚好食 平靚正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但景點黎講我自己覺得唔特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地話就話去六日 頭尾搭飛機已經冇咗兩日 其實得四日玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住得兩日半係喺札幌 我諗都去唔到咁遠<br />\n<br />\n咁巴打你覺得札幌半日會唔會多"},{"pid":"8122373655c70f01c41d66f21d168ec00ddcc6cf","tid":50800,"uid":9410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T03:02:37.000Z","msg":"旭川我覺得值得去，冬天又有企鵝散步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好得